OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,FA charity is urging dog owners in
OL,7,FCumbria to consider signing them up to
OL,8,Fbecome life-saving blood donors.
OL,10,FPet Blood Bank UK, a charity which
OL,11,Fprovides blood to vets to be used for
OL,12,Fblood transfusions, is calling for
OL,13,Fmore dogs to put their best paw
OL,14,Fforward to save another.
OL,16,FBlood transfusions can be critical for
OL,17,Fanimals suffering from accidents,
OL,18,Fsurgery complications or serious
OL,19,Fillnesses.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
