PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,FHealthy dogs aged between one and
OL,7,Fnine, and weighing over 25kg are
OL,8,Feligible to sign up.
OL,10,FA 10 minute donation session can
OL,11,Fpotentially save up to three dogs in
OL,12,Fneed.
OL,14,FMacaila Finch and her dog Florrie have
OL,15,Fdonated seven times at the Frame and
OL,16,FSwift veterinary practice in Penrith.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,FMacaila said: "We had a friend who
OL,7,Fworks for the vets here, and another
OL,8,Ffriend who also had the job got
OL,9,Fdonated so we just thought it would be
OL,10,Fa nice thing to do to try and help
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,F"It's a really proud moment when she's
OL,14,Fleft here and she walks around proudly
OL,15,Fwith a little bandana on... it's
OL,16,Freally nice to think that she's doing
OL,17,Fsome good."
OL,19,FAlex Watson joined the charity after
OL,20,Fher dog Flash was saved thanks to
OL,21,Fblood donation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,FShe said: "It turned out that his
OL,7,Fimmune system had started attacking
OL,8,Fhis red blood cells. He became
OL,9,Fseverely anaemic and needed a blood
OL,10,Ftransfusion as a matter of life and or
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"It was just miraculous to seeing the
OL,14,Flife blood come back into him. Once he
OL,15,Fgot better, I decided I will try and
OL,16,Fdo what I could.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,F"One of my dogs was suitable to be a
OL,7,Fdonor so I signed them up and soon
OL,8,Fafter that I joined the team and
OL,9,Fstarted working on the donation
OL,10,Fsessions."
OL,12,FA dog can donate every eight weeks at
OL,13,Fsites across the UK, and donations are
OL,14,Ftransported to vets in emergency
OL,15,Fsituations.
OL,17,FSessions in the ITV Border region are
OL,18,Fheld in Kendal, Penrith and Workington.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
