FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,FVets pay for the blood at cost price
OL,7,Fand the charity is funded primarily
OL,8,Fthrough donations, fundraising, and
OL,9,Fsupport from veterinary practices.
OL,11,FDani Whitford, veterinary surgeon at
OL,12,FPet Blood Bank UK, said: "We are
OL,13,Fmanaging to meet the demand at the
OL,14,Fmoment, but we're always needing more.
OL,16,F"Some people maybe haven't heard of it
OL,17,Funtil they've had personal experiences
OL,18,Fwith it so that's often a foot in the
OL,19,Fdoor for donors, but this is why we're
OL,20,Ftrying to spread awareness about the
OL,21,Fthe charity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
