CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774271469
OL,3,CCall for dogs to put their best paw
OL,4,Cforward and become blood donors
OL,6,F"We really need more people who've got
OL,7,Fthe right dogs signing up and becoming
OL,8,Fdonors."
